SAVEPOINT Example

.................................

INSERT INTO Employee VALUES (1,'Sunil',50000);

SAVEPOINT sp1;

INSERT INTO Employee VALUES (2,'Anil',60000);

SAVEPOINT sp2;

INSERT INTO Employee VALUES (3,'Ravi',45000);

Current data:

eid	ename	salary
1	Sunil	50000
2	Anil	60000
3	Ravi	45000
Rollback to Savepoint
ROLLBACK TO sp2;
Result
eid	ename	salary
1	Sunil	50000
2	Anil	60000

Record 3 is removed.





